<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>التي تصل القلوب وتحيط بها.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>[سورة الهمزة <span class="c2">(١٠٤)</span> : الآيات ٨ الى ٩]<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِنَّها عَلَيْهِمْ مُؤْصَدَةٌ <span class="c2">(٨)</span> فِي عَمَدٍ مُمَدَّدَةٍ <span class="c2">(٩)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٨-<span class="c5"> إِنَّها عَلَيْهِمْ مُؤْصَدَةٌ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مُؤْصَدَةٌ مغلقة الأبواب.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٩-<span class="c5"> فِي عَمَدٍ مُمَدَّدَةٍ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فِي عَمَدٍ وهم مشدودون إلى عمد.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مُمَدَّدَةٍ ممدودة، فلا حركة لهم فيها ولا خلاص.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>